1.title: Blind Auditions 1
1.plot: The first blind audition of the sixth season. The coaches that have returned for this years season are Marco Borsato and Ali B, while Anouk and Sanne Hans are being introduced as coaches for the very first time. Anouk was from the beginning already very judgemental towards the contestants, which led to some irritation coming from Marco Borsato.

1.title: Blind Auditions 1
1.plot: The first blind audition of this season. The judges this year are Ali B, Anouk, Waylon and Sanne. Ali B was talking a lot about how Waylon gets all the pretty women in his team and Anouk thought Ali B was talking a little bit too much anyway.

2.title: Blind Auditions 2
2.plot: It was the second blind audition of this season. The coaches this year are: Ali B, Waylon, Sanne Hans and Anouk. These coaches will turn around in their chair when they hear a performer they want in their team. If there are more coaches who want a performer, he or she gets to choose who they want as their coach.

3.title: Blind Auditions 3
3.plot: It was the third blind audition of this season. The coaches this year are: Ali B, Waylon, Sanne Hans and Anouk. These coaches will turn around in their chair when they hear a performer they want in their team. If there are more coaches who want a performer, he or she gets to choose who they want as their coach.

4.title: Blind Auditions 4
4.plot: It was the fourth audition of the season and Anouk, Waylon, Ali B and Sanne are the coaches. The people who auditioned this episode and the songs they sang were: Valerie Timmermans (19) - One night only / Vington (25) - Book of love / Rose Marin (17) - When you say nothing at all / Katharina Wildenbeest (25) - Mesmerized / Tina Rama (20) - Issues / Sebastiën van Dorp (22) - Someone like you / Cassidy Roeks (21) - Edge of glory / Deborah de Groot (28) - Stil in mij / Maud Nieuwenhuis (17) - Flashlight / Remedy (24 and 26) - Me and my broken heart & lonely no more / Gin...

5.title: Blind Auditions 5
5.plot: It was the fifth blind audition of the season and the coaches this year are Ali B, Sanne, Waylon and Anouk. At the end of this episode we had a suprise visit of The Voice of Holland last year's runner up, Vinchenzo Tahaparay. Ali B brought Vinchenzo to the stage to convince one of the contestants that Team Ali B is the best team there is and she should join it.

6.title: Blind Auditions 6
6.plot: It was the sixth audition of the season and the coaches are Sanne, Ali B, Waylon and Anouk. The people who auditioned this episode and the songs they sang were: Milou Hesselink (23) - Woman / Gideon Luciana (20) - The A team / Aïsha Echteld (18) - Unfaithful / Berenice van Leer (37) - Teardrops / Tessa Looijen (22) - This is the last time / Joy van Keep (18) - Nobody's perfect / Amber Winter (20) - Dangerous woman / Pieter van der Zweep (28) - De waarheid / Karima Lemghari (43) - The boss / Mark Pathuis (30) - Het is over / Nikita Pellencau (18) - Stay / Bram Houg (22...

7.title: Blind Auditions 7
7.plot: It was the seventh and final blind audition of this season. The coaches this year are: Ali B, Waylon, Sanne Hans and Anouk. These coaches will turn around in their chair when they hear a performer they want in their team. If there are more coaches who want a performer, he or she gets to choose who they want as their coach.

imdb.plot outline: Four wellknown Dutch musicians search for the best voices in the Netherlands. Blind auditions allow them to select their teams based solely on the vocal qualities of the contestant. Over the course of several weeks they will mentor these singers to become artists while pitting the contestants against each other in battles. Who will be the ultimate Voice of Holland?
